        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Retire dependency registry scans",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Stop scheduling dependency registry existence scans after skill publish.\n- Delete the dependency registry scanner action, parser/cache helper, generated function references, and scanner-specific tests.\n- Remove dependency registry signal output from the HTTP API, docs, CLI fixtures, and tests.\n- Add an admin-only guarded cleanup action for the stored dependency registry scan data.\n- Keep the legacy dependency registry schema fields, cache table, and scan-status index so existing production data remains valid until an approved cleanup runs.\n- Remove the old dependency-registry static finding reason code from active scanner output.\n\nNo production cleanup command has been run. This PR removes scanner code and public/API output, but it does not delete stored dependency registry data by itself.\n\n## Cleanup command\n\nDry-run first:\n\n```bash\nbunx convex run maintenance:cleanupDependencyRegistryScanData '{\"dryRun\":true,\"batchSize\":100,\"maxBatches\":20}' --prod\n```\n\nApply only after reviewing dry-run output and approving the delete:\n\n```bash\nbunx convex run maintenance:cleanupDependencyRegistryScanData '{\"dryRun\":false,\"confirm\":\"delete-dependency-registry-scan-data\",\"batchSize\":100,\"maxBatches\":1}' --prod\n```\n\nThe apply path requires the exact confirmation token and only patches/deletes IDs returned by the cleanup page query:\n\n- unsets `skillVersions.depRegistryAnalysis`\n- unsets `skillVersions.depRegistryScanStatus`\n- removes `suspicious.dep_not_found_on_registry` from legacy static scan findings/reason codes\n- removes that same retired code from skill moderation reason/evidence fields\n- deletes `depRegistryCache` rows by row ID\n\n## Validation\n\n- `bunx convex codegen`\n- `bun run test -- convex/httpApiV1.handlers.test.ts convex/maintenance.test.ts --reporter=dot` — 313 passed\n- `bun run --cwd packages/clawhub test:src -- src/cli/commands/inspect.test.ts --reporter=dot` — 12 passed\n- `bun run test -- convex/lib/skillPublish.test.ts --reporter=dot --environment=node` — 7 passed\n- `bun run format:check`\n- `bun run lint`\n- `bunx tsc --noEmit --pretty false`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/schema/tsconfig.json --noEmit --pretty false`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/clawhub/tsconfig.json --noEmit --pretty false`\n- `git diff --check HEAD^`\n\nFull root Vitest did not complete locally because jsdom workers failed to start with `ERR_REQUIRE_ESM` from `html-encoding-sniffer` requiring ESM `@exodus/bytes/encoding-lite.js`. Focused suites above passed.\n",
